Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:58.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:04.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.71,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
