Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:59.07,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ直ぐに歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:07.15,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用なこの心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:21.67,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偽りないその目に映る暖かい光りを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:26.72,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,溢れる希望の中で今僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:32.17,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どれだけの愛に出逢えるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:38.98,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ時を今生きている愛すると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:44.32,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,思う喜び に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:59.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直地一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:07.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我這顆笨拙的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:21.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,感受著你的真誠雙眼所發出的溫暖光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:26.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴在滿溢而出的希望中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:32.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們究竟能遇見多深沉的愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:38.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活在當下 愛在此時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:44.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此想來 不禁欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正月的時候完全忘了要把這個拿給猛男同學的媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一月一日那天 我整個人都暈乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你親手送出 她會更高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打掃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生你的時候也是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 大和小姐 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那媽媽我去買點米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 有幾公斤重？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是嘛 那麼這些也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:39.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}我那時候也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這麼多？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,475)\fad(0,0)}我的老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們家的男人們真的很愛操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是過度保護啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你看看母子手冊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體檢全部沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天我也想成為伯母這樣強大的媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 畢竟男人們都是膽小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人要自強不息才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？猛男同學很強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在他五歲的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等幼兒園校車的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個笨蛋居然跳進了車道裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然及時阻止了猛仔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是手臂卻擦傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且流了不少血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時猛仔就..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己每天又是淤青又是流血 還一副無所謂的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學小時候就很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個膽小鬼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很疼媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還有戀母情節嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人啊 出乎意料地脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要照看好他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:36.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,他出生的時候 整個病房都在拍手叫好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.99,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像聊得很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿月體檢的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護士小姐還把猛男抱起來說“橫綱駕到”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像獅子王裡面一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 ..那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你買了多少公斤的米回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多買點屯著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把錢包裡的錢全用光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼媽媽去醫院檢查了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 可別摔跤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀哎呀 謝謝你啊 大和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學出生時有4.3千克呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 老媽告訴你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說我是個早產兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生時不到2千克 整天待在透明的箱子裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為實在太小了 好像都沒法和媽媽一起出院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我現在超有活力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待小寶寶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上要生了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 又因為貧血而有變數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是寶寶的哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是想馬上要第二個的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在卻和哥哥差了不少歲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再生一個太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拿重物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院檢查沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕鬆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和出生的時候 只有我的一半重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像沒能和媽媽一起出院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 人的誕生和成長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是理所當然的易事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 孩子他媽 我來打掃浴室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高興你能長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生來就比別人個子大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長到現在也沒得過什麼大病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒有很深的感觸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這些並非理所當然的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都這麼愛操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可比不上猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有阿誠這樣善良的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有個可愛的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他是個好男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來還完全沒長大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望這孩子也能交上好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽可高興了 走路時都把它繫在包上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早點見到寶寶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看猛男同學的百日照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個姿勢好哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說有助於順產呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是沒錯啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過動作太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小傢夥在我肚子裡狠踢了一腳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來會生一個超有活力的寶寶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 孩子他媽 我來洗浴..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛嗎？是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我出去趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你要去幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散步啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了生個健康寶寶 要多走路才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話我跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這麼大了還母子一起散步很難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道爸爸媽媽為什麼結婚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和媽媽是同期進入公司的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一股完全不像新員工的氣度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作賣力 又受上司青睞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有女員工都很仰賴她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那年的忘年會上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹中小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把土瓶蒸依次遞過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很燙要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百合子醬 你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 倒是你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去洗一洗 沒事的我穿得很厚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿點冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那種可愛的女孩 就不由得會想保護她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時 爸爸有生以來頭一回..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要和這個人一起跨越人生的巨浪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要一起打高爾夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰板果然很扎實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去兜風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想守護竹中小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過媽媽她是個女強人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還從沒需要我保護過呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太明天也要去檢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 我們倆都快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 那明天..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不知道是男是女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我完全猜不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是女孩子倒是有點難以想象呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼都只能想象出和你一樣的臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這裡要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟或者妹妹..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 想到的都是同一張臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 你笑過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寶寶又在裡面踢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔..叫出租車..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽..要去一趟醫院..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有出租車..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到好大的動靜..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽她..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}咚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}那時的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}嗚哇哇哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.33,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}誒？出血了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}那麼我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}小不小？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}出生100天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}年糕華夫餅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}這是100天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}圓滾滾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}舊姓\N竹中百合子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:35.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}噗
