Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 用電話叫車就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸在公司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要振作一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 請問要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼做 做什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請去志須田綜合醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔 媽媽把錢包忘在家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車費我已經付了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿誠真是可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢包在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在衣櫃上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真希望他能冷靜一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是猛男的優點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和大和小姐都太寵猛男了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生正在幫她檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜 要冷靜 阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才要冷靜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟她總是很精神的..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種樣子..我是頭一回看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔 你把錢包拿來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你和寶寶都沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽要直接住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住院..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來有些事要拜託你做 做個筆記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住院行李都已經整好放在我的房間了 幫忙拿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來是把碗盤洗了 還有洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而明天是可燃垃圾日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸那邊我會打電話的..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 別擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶您去病房哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把東西送去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太在203號室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太太她現在在檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李放我這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂他 回去了嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到了砂川同學的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說伯母住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以借用廚房嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做咖喱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地去買食材來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 不削皮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 這個是漂白水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會太甜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡吃偏甜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用送我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學就待在家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有困難就叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上會過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是猛男做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是大和幫我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸去過醫院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽她怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟或妹妹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 沒事 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天放學時去趟醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 還好有猛男在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遇到一位同產期的孕婦朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在我面前差點摔倒 我連忙去扶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果肚子就有些疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能坐視不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子裡的孩子是不是在生我的氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 因為雙方你都想保護吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼下面翻到教科書53頁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來讀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要振作才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院發來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須振作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要用跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔 你幹嘛這麼擔心的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我又不是病人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼事要我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼幫我去買水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 她的臉色好差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且出了不少汗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過畢竟要從一個人的肚子裡冒出另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出產這種事..一定非常辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼我能幫忙的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 伯母她怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 有我在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院在2樓對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟臉啊 我已經長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在努力的是小寶寶和老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我去為老媽打打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 阿砂和大和來看望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔 用呼叫器叫護士來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陣痛忍太久了..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 呼叫器在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 請問有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快過來 要出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產婦好像走不動了 拜託帶輪椅來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是哥哥 要健康地生下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等著你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我也要輪椅..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田夫人 輪椅來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把隔壁的孕婦太太推過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是頭胎 會比較不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太你沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽由我來抱過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 我會跟著你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥會穩穩地抱你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的朋友 還有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都很想見到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽也都等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心出生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,託剛田太太的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子在昨天健康出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生下來之後 請和這孩子交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友也在等著你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛仔 把媽媽的黑色包包拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我去生個就來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好期待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐著等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛田太太生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順產成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個4.2千克的健康女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位爸爸 您夫人很努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 恭喜你 這位爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4.2千克這麼重..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過和其他孩子比起來大了兩圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到真正的初生寶寶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許給你也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生來比別人有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長得比別人高大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 將來我想做幫助人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到竟然會有被猛男公主抱的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為他還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不知不覺間已經長大成人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再努力把另一個也拉扯大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字取什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小寶寶真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級可愛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 好小哦 好溫暖好柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 有指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懷抱小寶寶的大和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為保育員或者助產士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個 是文理不同科系的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這麼無趣的話啦 阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 你想讓妹妹怎麼叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是歐尼醬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 還有“哥哥”之類的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你“猛男”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也挺好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:25.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 難道是注重養生之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}猛男同學家的鍋子好重！鐵的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.43,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}洗衣液是這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}嘴角沾太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}洗碗精用太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}啊哈哈 猛男同學洗碗洗出好多泡泡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}嗯！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.21,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}還有咖喱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.21,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}今天也可以去你家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.21,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}咖喱還有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.16,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}我現在要去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.16,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.16,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}咖喱已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}我也能去醫院探望嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}那當然！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}老媽她也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}那我來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:23.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}婦產科
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:23.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}剛田百合子！！夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}吃飯時間到了哦 還要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}噢啦噢啦 還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}哦 老媽好強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.93,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}他不是孩子他爸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}他不是孩子他爸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:51.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}剛田百合子媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}睡得好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.72,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}年紀差太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:29.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}好籠統啊
